# Public API the Electron/browser app calls (gateway OR main-server — never raw RAG :8082).
# RAG at http://192.168.0.34:8082 is reached by main-server only (ragserver.base-url in application.yml).
#
# Defaults are driven by src/config/serverProfile.ts (ACTIVE_SERVER_PROFILE). Uncomment to override:

# Option A — API gateway (preferred: frontend → gateway → main-server)
#VITE_API_BASE=http://192.168.0.10:8080

# If the gateway does NOT proxy /rag/* to main-server (404 on /rag/ingest), point RAG at main-server:
#VITE_RAG_BASE=http://192.168.0.34:8081

# Option B — direct to main-server only if you intentionally bypass the gateway (replace host as needed)
#VITE_API_BASE=http://192.168.0.34:8081
